{"tid":2236527,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[藍屍為所欲為，恐嚇都唔咬]4人涉「和你lunch」打鬥　兩人擬認罪但案情不符　官斥控方準備不足浪費時間","createTime":"2020-10-09T14:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T07:16:23.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfdde09498a01ec16d43607eb4e22e6b64f03993","tid":2236527,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201009/s00001/1602238892431/4%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%89%e3%80%8c%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%a0lunch%e3%80%8d%e6%89%93%e9%ac%a5-%e5%85%a9%e4%ba%ba%e6%93%ac%e8%aa%8d%e7%bd%aa%e4%bd%86%e6%a1%88%e6%83%85%e4%b8%8d%e7%ac%a6-%e5%ae%98%e6%96%a5%e6%8e%a7%e6%96%b9%e6%ba%96%e5%82%99%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b3%e6%b5%aa%e8%b2%bb%e6%99%82%e9%96%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F1602238892431%2F4%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25b6%2589%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2592%258c%25e4%25bd%25a0lunch%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2589%2593%25e9%25ac%25a5-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2593%25ac%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e4%25bd%2586%25e6%25a1%2588%25e6%2583%2585%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%25ac%25a6-%25e5%25ae%2598%25e6%2596%25a5%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25ba%2596%25e5%2582%2599%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%25b6%25b3%25e6%25b5%25aa%25e8%25b2%25bb%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2596%2593&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzgi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=2fdfe47e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F1602238892431%2F4%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25b6%2589%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2592%258c%25e4%25bd%25a0lunch%25e3%2580%258d%25e6%2589%2593%25e9%25ac%25a5-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%2593%25ac%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%25bd%25aa%25e4%25bd%2586%25e6%25a1%2588%25e6%2583%2585%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%25ac%25a6-%25e5%25ae%2598%25e6%2596%25a5%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%2596%25b9%25e6%25ba%2596%25e5%2582%2599%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%25b6%25b3%25e6%25b5%25aa%25e8%25b2%25bb%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2596%2593&h=4ac5ad2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201009/s00001/1602238892431/4%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%89%e3%80%8c%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%a0lunch%e3%80%8d%e6%89%93%e9%ac%a5-%e5%85%a9%e4%ba%ba%e6%93%ac%e8%aa%8d%e7%bd%aa%e4%bd%86%e6%a1%88%e6%83%85%e4%b8%8d%e7%ac%a6-%e5%ae%98%e6%96%a5%e6%8e%a7%e6%96%b9%e6%ba%96%e5%82%99%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b3%e6%b5%aa%e8%b2%bb%e6%99%82%e9%96%93</a><br />\n<br />\n今年2月銅鑼灣時代廣場「和你lunch」活動期間，一批手持國旗巿民與示威者起爭執，被稱為「正義姐」的女子藍雪寶疑遭襲擊，兩青年事後被捕，另兩名疑為建制支持者的中年女子亦被控在公眾地方打鬥。4人之中，兩人今日（9日）在東區裁判法院擬認罪，惟裁判官稱控方準備不周，納入與認罪被告不相干的案情，斥檢控官「浪費時間」。擬認罪兩人未被定罪，案件押後至10月16日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n案中4名被告依次分別為學生蔡俊軒（23歲）、無業的黃卓熙（20歲）、售貨員李秋芝（42歲）、商人宋晞綸（45歲）。其中蔡俊軒庭上否認傷人罪；黃卓熙、李秋芝及宋晞綸則被控「在公眾地方打鬥」罪，黃卓熙、李秋芝認罪，宋晞綸則不認罪。<br />\n<br />\n惟主任裁判官錢禮稱，兩名擬認罪被告的案情涉及案發其他人的行為，問控方該些行為與黃卓熙及李秋芝「有何相干」，又問「叫認罪兩人如何承認」？<br />\n<br />\n控方要求押後案件片刻，惟錢官斥控方「浪費時間」，控方終要求押後案件，以索取指示，黃卓熙及李秋芝續獲保釋至10月16日再訊。至於不認罪的蔡俊軒及宋晞綸，兩人的案件排期至12月15日開審。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>案件散庭後，被告李秋芝的親友疑不滿記者拍攝辱罵記者，更追趕記者至法院外100米路段，其間推撞及腳踩一名女記者，當中有人更向一在場另一記者說「準備受靶」、「行唔出西灣河」，另有人近距離拍攝記者容貌。警方接報到場稱事件純屬意外，着涉事的人向記者道歉了事。<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201009/s00001/8159a216bd8fece1c7faea80c924374f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F8159a216bd8fece1c7faea80c924374f.jpg&h=4728e5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3之1 - 第三被告李秋芝（白衣白褲者）（明報記者攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201009/s00001/81cae663a208a6a39c55b66ef69cc311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F81cae663a208a6a39c55b66ef69cc311.jpg&h=5365be12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3之2 - 涉推撞女記者的男子（明報記者攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201009/s00001/81ca05130aa4304917c0d3cb61ca6434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F81ca05130aa4304917c0d3cb61ca6434.jpg&h=7f946d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖3之3 - 涉向在場另一記者說「準備受靶」、「行唔出西灣河」的男子（右）（明報記者攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201009/s00001/8159a216bd8fece1c7faea80c924374f.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F8159a216bd8fece1c7faea80c924374f.jpg&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzgi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=478c0e1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201009%2Fs00001%2F8159a216bd8fece1c7faea80c924374f.jpg&h=596c1d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201009/s00001/8159a216bd8fece1c7faea80c924374f.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"e6a79734d93784a0c9c4904b2af7479b3b20fe5d","tid":2236527,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"藍屍為所欲為"},{"pid":"3358ebf78b34b7c471ec9dfbe6e322cc10a6a541","tid":2236527,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:54:50.000Z","msg":"再推下全樣"},{"pid":"00c3642fec677b797cb0008460ab54a89c12339e","tid":2236527,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1059601453c68b842fed4182ad3101223a7b651","tid":2236527,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"為所欲為呀"}]}